168
00:08:18,398 --> 00:08:20,100
♪ Unlock your disk ♪

169
00:08:20,100 --> 00:08:22,035
♪ Leave the Black Dinos
on every conquest ♪

170
00:08:22,035 --> 00:08:23,436
♪ Unlock your disk ♪

171
00:08:23,436 --> 00:08:25,105
♪ Little Spot Dino
is harmless enough ♪

172
00:08:25,105 --> 00:08:26,940
♪ To unlock the Kuro,
you gotta be tough ♪

173
00:08:26,940 --> 00:08:28,608
♪ Captain Kuro
will stomp and brawl ♪

174
00:08:28,608 --> 00:08:30,677
♪ These monsters rule,
unlock 'em all ♪

175
00:08:30,677 --> 00:08:32,312
♪ Unlock it, unlock it ♪

176
00:08:32,312 --> 00:08:34,514
♪ Unlock your disk ♪

177
00:08:34,514 --> 00:08:36,282
♪ Monsters rule ♪

178
00:08:40,420 --> 00:08:43,156
Okay, everybody.

179
00:08:43,156 --> 00:08:46,226
(chewing)

180
00:08:46,226 --> 00:08:48,261
Not hungry, Suezo?

181
00:08:48,261 --> 00:08:52,999
No, I think I'll just go up
and get a breath of fresh air.

182
00:08:52,999 --> 00:08:54,034
Hey, what's wrong?

183
00:08:54,034 --> 00:08:56,369
‐Nothing.
‐Nothing?

184
00:08:56,369 --> 00:08:57,437
Karma.

185
00:08:57,437 --> 00:08:58,705
What do you mean?

186
00:08:58,705 --> 00:09:01,307
Ah, he had to
work for a change.

187
00:09:01,307 --> 00:09:04,444
Nope, Suezo's seasick.

188
00:09:04,444 --> 00:09:05,512
(grumbling)

189
00:09:05,512 --> 00:09:07,680
‐Golem.
‐Hmm?

190
00:09:07,680 --> 00:09:09,249
Holly.

191
00:09:09,249 --> 00:09:11,751
Hey, do you want some dinner?

192
00:09:11,751 --> 00:09:13,019
No.

193
00:09:13,019 --> 00:09:14,054
Oh.

194
00:09:14,054 --> 00:09:16,022
Well there's some
yummy rocks and stones

195
00:09:16,022 --> 00:09:17,824
for you to eat down below.

196
00:09:17,824 --> 00:09:21,094
Golem likes it right here.

197
00:09:21,094 --> 00:09:21,961
'Kay.

198
00:09:21,961 --> 00:09:24,864
♪

199
00:09:24,864 --> 00:09:27,700
The stars are beautiful.

200
00:09:27,700 --> 00:09:30,203
A lot's happened since we
started this adventure,

201
00:09:30,203 --> 00:09:31,971
hasn't it, Golem?

202
00:09:31,971 --> 00:09:33,540
Yes.

203
00:09:33,540 --> 00:09:35,742
I hate to admit it,
but sometimes I worry

204
00:09:35,742 --> 00:09:38,578
that we're never
going to find the Phoenix.

205
00:09:38,578 --> 00:09:39,746
Hmm?

206
00:09:39,746 --> 00:09:42,315
The land across the sea
is a strange place

207
00:09:42,315 --> 00:09:44,517
where they say Moo's
rule is even stronger

208
00:09:44,517 --> 00:09:46,086
than where we've been.

209
00:09:46,086 --> 00:09:48,988
The powers of the baddies
are probably stronger, too.

210
00:09:48,988 --> 00:09:50,924
Don't worry, Holly.

211
00:09:50,924 --> 00:09:52,559
We will find the Phoenix.

212
00:09:52,559 --> 00:09:53,760
Huh?

213
00:09:53,760 --> 00:09:56,129
We have learned
something important,

214
00:09:56,129 --> 00:09:59,732
that when we work together
as a team, we can win.

215
00:09:59,732 --> 00:10:02,168
We will find the Phoenix.

216
00:10:02,168 --> 00:10:04,671
You're right, yes we will.

217
00:10:04,671 --> 00:10:07,707
You feel better now, Holly?

218
00:10:07,707 --> 00:10:09,943
Thanks, Golem, I certainly do.

219
00:10:09,943 --> 00:10:19,152
♪

220
00:10:19,152 --> 00:10:23,089
(snoring)

221
00:10:23,089 --> 00:10:26,126
Oh, here we go again.

222
00:10:26,126 --> 00:10:28,761
Suezo?

223
00:10:28,761 --> 00:10:31,264
(waves crashing)

224
00:10:31,264 --> 00:10:33,633
Ah!

225
00:10:33,633 --> 00:10:35,802
♪

226
00:10:35,802 --> 00:10:37,770
(yelling)

227
00:10:37,770 --> 00:10:40,673
♪

228
00:10:40,673 --> 00:10:42,842
Zilla!

229
00:10:42,842 --> 00:10:45,945
(yelling)

230
00:10:45,945 --> 00:10:51,417
♪

231
00:10:51,417 --> 00:10:53,887
Zillas off the
starboard bow, Captain!

232
00:10:53,887 --> 00:10:55,488
I can see that!

233
00:10:55,488 --> 00:10:58,424
Send your lads, Guji?

234
00:10:58,424 --> 00:11:01,227
(ship creaking)

235
00:11:01,227 --> 00:11:05,899
♪

236
00:11:05,899 --> 00:11:10,336
Time to settle this yourself,
you skylarking hooligan!

237
00:11:10,336 --> 00:11:14,073
(growling)

238
00:11:14,073 --> 00:11:16,009
Let the games begin!

239
00:11:16,009 --> 00:11:16,910
Argh!

240
00:11:16,910 --> 00:11:19,045
More of Moo's baddies!

241
00:11:19,045 --> 00:11:23,249
(growling)

242
00:11:23,249 --> 00:11:24,484
And fire!

243
00:11:24,484 --> 00:11:26,452
(cannon fire)

244
00:11:26,452 --> 00:11:32,292
♪

245
00:11:32,292 --> 00:11:33,226
Ready?

246
00:11:33,226 --> 00:11:34,561
Chi.

247
00:11:34,561 --> 00:11:35,862
(cannon fire)

248
00:11:35,862 --> 00:11:38,531
Can't swim.

249
00:11:38,531 --> 00:11:41,634
♪

250
00:11:41,634 --> 00:11:43,069
It's okay, Golem.

251
00:11:43,069 --> 00:11:44,671
This ship's not going down.

252
00:11:44,671 --> 00:11:46,339
Thank you, Holly.

253
00:11:46,339 --> 00:11:48,508
We're a team,
remember, Golem?

254
00:11:48,508 --> 00:11:50,777
And that's what teammates do.

255
00:11:50,777 --> 00:11:52,412
Because we can
do things together

256
00:11:52,412 --> 00:11:54,047
we can't do by ourselves.

257
00:11:54,047 --> 00:11:56,082
Right, Holly.

258
00:11:56,082 --> 00:11:58,017
Hmm.

259
00:11:58,017 --> 00:12:00,320
Give it all you got, men!

260
00:12:00,320 --> 00:12:02,889
Defeat those Zillas!

261
00:12:02,889 --> 00:12:05,858
♪

262
00:12:05,858 --> 00:12:08,962
Zilla troops move forward,
don't let up!

263
00:12:08,962 --> 00:12:10,563
Attack, attack, Zillas!

264
00:12:10,563 --> 00:12:11,631
It's no good.

265
00:12:11,631 --> 00:12:14,234
The enemy is stronger
than we are.

266
00:12:14,234 --> 00:12:15,301
We are Zillas!

267
00:12:15,301 --> 00:12:17,270
We never retreat!

268
00:12:17,270 --> 00:12:18,972
We must attack now!

269
00:12:18,972 --> 00:12:20,807
(cannon fire)

270
00:12:20,807 --> 00:12:21,908
Yeah, right.

271
00:12:21,908 --> 00:12:27,247
Come back, you‐‐here.

272
00:12:27,247 --> 00:12:29,115
Still want to attack?

273
00:12:29,115 --> 00:12:32,485
Grrr, what do you think?

274
00:12:32,485 --> 00:12:34,354
What are your orders, Zilla?

275
00:12:34,354 --> 00:12:37,223
Retreat!

276
00:12:37,223 --> 00:12:39,859
(grumbling)

277
00:12:39,859 --> 00:12:42,962
(laughing)

278
00:12:42,962 --> 00:12:44,097
♪

279
00:12:44,097 --> 00:12:45,598
We did it!

280
00:12:45,598 --> 00:12:48,735
Mocchi!

281
00:12:48,735 --> 00:12:58,544
♪

282
00:12:58,544 --> 00:13:00,246
(trembling)

283
00:13:00,246 --> 00:13:06,586
♪

284
00:13:06,586 --> 00:13:11,024
Looks like I'll have to
take care of this myself.

285
00:13:11,024 --> 00:13:12,892
Well, blow me down.

286
00:13:12,892 --> 00:13:14,827
Hey, Captain, what's going on?

287
00:13:14,827 --> 00:13:15,995
I can feel it.

288
00:13:15,995 --> 00:13:20,700
Me horn is telling me that
Monster Guji is on his way here.

289
00:13:20,700 --> 00:13:21,834
(all together)
Gugi!

290
00:13:21,834 --> 00:13:25,738
The foulest scourge
to ever swim the briny deep.

291
00:13:25,738 --> 00:13:28,441
He'd sink a ship
as soon as to look at it

292
00:13:28,441 --> 00:13:31,077
and he's tried
to sink many of mine.

293
00:13:31,077 --> 00:13:32,312
We'll take care of him.

294
00:13:32,312 --> 00:13:33,446
Chi!

295
00:13:33,446 --> 00:13:44,624
♪

296
00:13:44,624 --> 00:13:46,793
(yelling)

297
00:13:50,463 --> 00:13:53,733
You've come
at last, Guji, hey?

298
00:13:53,733 --> 00:13:55,001
That's Guji?

299
00:13:55,001 --> 00:13:56,436
He's enormous.

300
00:13:56,436 --> 00:13:59,972
That's a really big monster!

301
00:13:59,972 --> 00:14:04,077
So, Captain,
nice to see you again.

302
00:14:04,077 --> 00:14:05,645
Zilla!

303
00:14:05,645 --> 00:14:08,347
♪

304
00:14:08,347 --> 00:14:09,782
And blast 'em!

305
00:14:09,782 --> 00:14:11,717
(cannon fire)

306
00:14:11,717 --> 00:14:14,587
And blast 'em again,
me hearties.

307
00:14:14,587 --> 00:14:17,857
♪

308
00:14:17,857 --> 00:14:20,526
(yelling)

309
00:14:20,526 --> 00:14:22,528
♪

310
00:14:22,528 --> 00:14:24,063
(evil laughter)

311
00:14:24,063 --> 00:14:26,899
Difficult to believe
a puny creature like you

312
00:14:26,899 --> 00:14:29,535
could upset
Master Moo so much.

313
00:14:29,535 --> 00:14:34,707
♪

314
00:14:34,707 --> 00:14:35,875
Don't worry, Holly,

315
00:14:35,875 --> 00:14:39,278
Captain Horn will protect you.

316
00:14:39,278 --> 00:14:40,813
Argh!

317
00:14:40,813 --> 00:14:42,582
Captain Horn!

318
00:14:42,582 --> 00:14:44,117
(screaming)

319
00:14:44,117 --> 00:14:45,184
Holly!

320
00:14:45,184 --> 00:14:47,120
Oh no, you don't!

321
00:14:47,120 --> 00:14:49,122
Pick on someone your own size,

322
00:14:49,122 --> 00:14:50,123
‐you bully.
‐Don't you know

323
00:14:50,123 --> 00:14:53,559
you're messing with
the monster champ, Guji?

324
00:14:53,559 --> 00:14:56,329
Alley oop!

325
00:14:56,329 --> 00:14:58,598
Rip it up!

326
00:14:58,598 --> 00:15:01,033
♪

327
00:15:01,033 --> 00:15:02,468
Arrgh!

328
00:15:02,468 --> 00:15:04,837
Agghh!

329
00:15:04,837 --> 00:15:07,073
♪

330
00:15:07,073 --> 00:15:10,343
Genki, you okay, kid?

331
00:15:10,343 --> 00:15:12,979
Sure, I'm the champ, remember?

332
00:15:12,979 --> 00:15:15,615
You just got me
real mad, Guji,

333
00:15:15,615 --> 00:15:18,651
and you really don't
want to see me mad!

334
00:15:18,651 --> 00:15:23,756
Yah, and I'm with him,
you scurvy‐faced hooligan!

335
00:15:23,756 --> 00:15:25,925
Hey, put her down!

336
00:15:25,925 --> 00:15:28,861
I must help her.

337
00:15:28,861 --> 00:15:31,731
♪

338
00:15:31,731 --> 00:15:33,766
Would some of you
bothersome gnats

339
00:15:33,766 --> 00:15:36,502
care to join
the young lady, perhaps?

340
00:15:36,502 --> 00:15:38,004
(yelling)

341
00:15:38,004 --> 00:15:44,744
♪

342
00:15:44,744 --> 00:15:45,711
Chi!

343
00:15:45,711 --> 00:15:47,046
It's Golem!

344
00:15:47,046 --> 00:15:51,651
One for all,
and all for one.

345
00:15:51,651 --> 00:15:55,421
(struggling)

346
00:15:55,421 --> 00:15:57,657
♪

347
00:15:57,657 --> 00:15:58,791
Tornado!

348
00:15:58,791 --> 00:16:01,160
♪

349
00:16:01,160 --> 00:16:02,361
(screaming)

350
00:16:02,361 --> 00:16:04,931
(together)
Holly, I will catch you!

351
00:16:04,931 --> 00:16:06,132
(screaming)

352
00:16:06,132 --> 00:16:13,372
♪

353
00:16:13,372 --> 00:16:15,474
Tornado!

354
00:16:15,474 --> 00:16:22,048
♪

355
00:16:22,048 --> 00:16:24,483
Rope 'im, me lads.

356
00:16:24,483 --> 00:16:36,896
♪

357
00:16:36,896 --> 00:16:41,100
Arm the halyards,
full speed ahead, me hearties.

358
00:16:41,100 --> 00:16:47,506
♪

359
00:16:47,506 --> 00:16:49,909
You'll get off here.

360
00:16:49,909 --> 00:16:53,312
Then we'll decide
this once and for all.

361
00:16:53,312 --> 00:16:56,048
This Monster Guji
must be stopped.

362
00:16:56,048 --> 00:16:59,352
(yelling)

363
00:16:59,352 --> 00:17:04,590
♪

364
00:17:04,590 --> 00:17:07,793
(yelling encouragements)

365
00:17:07,793 --> 00:17:09,295
Chi!

366
00:17:09,295 --> 00:17:15,968
♪

367
00:17:15,968 --> 00:17:18,537
Hard to port!

368
00:17:18,537 --> 00:17:21,807
We'll drop him
into the whirlpool.

369
00:17:21,807 --> 00:17:29,682
♪

370
00:17:29,682 --> 00:17:32,518
Now then,
cut the blighter loose.

371
00:17:32,518 --> 00:17:37,456
♪

372
00:17:37,456 --> 00:17:40,092
I'm not finished
with you yet!

373
00:17:40,092 --> 00:17:41,661
♪

374
00:17:41,661 --> 00:17:42,962
Zilla!

375
00:17:42,962 --> 00:17:46,198
♪

376
00:17:46,198 --> 00:17:47,767
(yelling)

377
00:17:47,767 --> 00:17:52,038
Never underestimate
your enemy, Horn.

378
00:17:52,038 --> 00:17:56,542
♪

379
00:17:56,542 --> 00:17:58,878
(yelling)

380
00:17:58,878 --> 00:18:15,828
♪

381
00:18:15,828 --> 00:18:17,363
Fill the main sails!

382
00:18:17,363 --> 00:18:19,298
That whirlpool's close!

383
00:18:19,298 --> 00:18:31,110
♪

384
00:18:31,110 --> 00:18:32,311
Yeah!

385
00:18:32,311 --> 00:18:36,315
(celebrating)

386
00:18:36,315 --> 00:18:39,685
Golem, you saved us!

387
00:18:39,685 --> 00:18:41,554
It's just like
you said before,

388
00:18:41,554 --> 00:18:44,623
All for one
and one for all, right?

389
00:18:44,623 --> 00:18:46,592
(laughing)

390
00:18:46,592 --> 00:18:47,727
Congrats.

391
00:18:47,727 --> 00:18:49,595
Look what else
you've done, Golem.

392
00:18:49,595 --> 00:18:52,298
You've overcome
your fear of water.

393
00:18:52,298 --> 00:18:54,800
Oh?

394
00:18:54,800 --> 00:18:57,770
Aargh!

395
00:18:57,770 --> 00:18:59,405
Golem?

396
00:18:59,405 --> 00:19:03,909
Well, I suppose you can lead
a golem to water but maybe not.

397
00:19:03,909 --> 00:19:05,478
Ugh.

398
00:19:05,478 --> 00:19:07,847
♪

399
00:19:07,847 --> 00:19:11,717
(laughing)

400
00:19:11,717 --> 00:19:23,362
♪

401
00:19:23,362 --> 00:19:25,097
Look, there it is!

402
00:19:25,097 --> 00:19:37,109
♪

403
00:19:37,109 --> 00:19:38,911
Thanks a lot
for your help, Horn.

404
00:19:38,911 --> 00:19:41,313
Ah, we couldn't have
stopped Guji without you,

405
00:19:41,313 --> 00:19:43,849
so thanks yourself, me boy.

406
00:19:43,849 --> 00:19:46,619
And here...

407
00:19:46,619 --> 00:19:47,353
What?

408
00:19:47,353 --> 00:19:50,289
♪

409
00:19:50,289 --> 00:19:51,257
Wow!

410
00:19:51,257 --> 00:19:53,125
It may be of help.

411
00:19:53,125 --> 00:19:55,428
♪

412
00:19:55,428 --> 00:19:56,729
It's great!

413
00:19:56,729 --> 00:19:58,431
Horn, where'd you go?

414
00:19:58,431 --> 00:20:02,201
That map is a farewell gift
for you all, Miss Holly.

415
00:20:02,201 --> 00:20:05,971
We'll treasure it, Horn,
thank you very much.

416
00:20:05,971 --> 00:20:09,108
(yelling)

417
00:20:09,108 --> 00:20:12,678
Come on, Miss Holly,
how about this side too, ah?

418
00:20:12,678 --> 00:20:15,080
Horn, just back right off!

419
00:20:15,080 --> 00:20:17,149
♪

420
00:20:17,149 --> 00:20:19,985
(all together)
Bye!

421
00:20:19,985 --> 00:20:27,993
♪

422
00:20:27,993 --> 00:20:30,296
And now, on with our search.

423
00:20:30,296 --> 00:20:33,933
♪

424
00:20:33,933 --> 00:20:36,635
All right, you better
look out, baddies,

425
00:20:36,635 --> 00:20:38,938
'cause we're gonna
find the Phoenix!

426
00:20:38,938 --> 00:20:41,407
(all together)
Yeah!

427
00:20:41,407 --> 00:20:45,945
♪

428
00:20:46,712 --> 00:20:47,646
♪ Monsters ♪

429
00:20:47,646 --> 00:20:49,482
♪ Monsters rule ♪

430
00:20:49,482 --> 00:21:14,039
♪

431
00:21:14,039 --> 00:21:15,941
♪ Monsters rule ♪

